1. PROPOSAL DETAILS

 This proposal intends to reduce the minimum required votes from a proposal to pass. 

 &nbsp; 

2. ECONOMIC IMPACT - None 

 &nbsp; 

3. IMPACT ON USERS - Users will have easier decision making because of the lowered threshold. 

 &nbsp; 

4. EXPECTED POSITIVE IMPACT - It will be easier to take decisions, also encourage people to participate in democracy with a lower threshold. 

&nbsp; 

5. KNOWN POTENTIAL OR NEGATIVE DOWNSIDES - Lower thresholds could mean easier entrance to harmful proposals if the community do not participate actively.
